### Calculate price — valid request (with percent coupon)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8337/calculate-price
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": 1,
  "taxNumber": "GR123456789",
  "couponCode": "P6"
}

###HTTP/1.1 422 Unprocessable Content
###
