###    "errors": {
###        "couponCode": "Coupon \"P6\" does not exist."
###    }
###}

### Calculate price — valid request (with fixed coupon)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8337/calculate-price
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": 1,
  "taxNumber": "IT12345678900",
  "couponCode": "D15"
}

###HTTP/1.1 200 OK
###
###{
###"price": 103.7
###}

### Calculate price — validation error (invalid taxNumber)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8337/calculate-price
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": 1,
  "taxNumber": "INVALID"
}

###HTTP/1.1 422 Unprocessable Content
###
