###}

### Purchase — valid request (paypal)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8337/purchase
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": 1,
  "taxNumber": "DE123456789",
  "paymentProcessor": "paypal"
}

###HTTP/1.1 200 OK
###
###{
###"message": "Payment successful"
###}

